data.description: Charming home nestled on a quiet street and surrounded by mountain views, just a block away from the Willamette River! Located in the heart of every outdoor enthusiast's dream with close proximity to mountain biking, hiking, walking trails, fishing, and so much more! Step inside and be greeted with plenty of natural light, new upgrades throughout including all new carpet in the bedrooms. Gorgeous kitchen with sealed butcher block countertops, and a brand new dishwasher to compliment the rest of stainless steel appliances. Enjoy breakfast in nook area or create a barista space of your own with the sensible built-ins. 3 bedrooms on the main and a sizable bonus upstairs w/ ample storage and smart LED lights throughout! Newer interior paint. 2 ductless units allowing for more efficient heating and cooling throughout the home. Fenced in backyard with fire pit and large finished shed with power currently used as office space! Roof and water heater less than 5 years old! Too many upgrades to list, call today for more information and to schedule your private showing!
